pel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden entryway with built-in storage, a leather bench, two hanging bags, a circular window, and a woven basket on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578512\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578512\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A tall, narrow pull-out pantry with shelves holding shoes, cleaning supplies, bottles, and baskets is built into the wall beside a wooden door in a modern kitchen.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBuilt in Poland and floated to its permanent site in Copenhagen, the structure features expansive glass walls that invite the harbor in, while carefully placed terraces offer outdoor sanctuaries above the waterline. The exterior is sheathed in dark wood cladding reminiscent of Garde Hvalsøe’s signature wardrobes, ensuring both privacy and harmony with the urban landscape.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578513\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578513\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wooden cabinets, black countertops, pendant lights, hanging pots, and a large window overlooking a red house and greenery outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578514\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578514\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-7-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wood cabinets, black countertops, pendant lights, built-in ovens, and large windows; potted plants sit on the windowsill and natural light fills the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-7-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-7.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInside, the space is a showcase of bespoke details and high-end materials. The kitchen, a focal point for Garde and his wife Rita, features handcrafted Garde Hvalsøe cabinetry, a dramatic stone countertop, and open displays of culinary tools that speak to the couple’s passion for cooking. Vintage furniture by Bruno Mathsson and Hans Wegner anchor the dining area in Scandinavian heritage, while contemporary lighting and minimalist design add a refined edge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578515\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578515\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wooden cabinets, a dark countertop, hanging pendant lights, and various kitchen appliances; large windows with plants on the sill provide natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“I love the process of creating something new, and by building from scratch, you get everything exactly as you want,” says Søren, who took the same approach to this project as he does his cabinetry company.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578516\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578516\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with light wood flooring, black cabinetry, a small black dining table with two chairs, and large windows letting in natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578517\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578517\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10-810x1037.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining area with wooden floors, glass doors, and outdoor seating visible through large windows. Simple furniture and neutral decor create a minimalist, airy atmosphere.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1037\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10-810x1037.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10-800x1024.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10-768x983.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10-1200x1536.jpg 1200w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMaterials throughout the houseboat reflect both luxury and longevity. From brass bathroom fixtures that will develop a natural patina over time to fine oak flooring by Dinesen and concrete surfaces, the palette is restrained but richly tactile. Even the shower, tiled in soft neutral tones, exudes a quiet elegance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578518\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578518\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining area with wooden furniture, large windows, and views of water and city buildings. Light wood floor and minimalist decor create a bright, airy atmosphere.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578519\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578519\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"View from inside a room through an open sliding door to a wooden deck with potted plants, outdoor seating, and a waterfront cityscape in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-11m.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578520\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578520\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-12-810x951.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with light wood floors, black leather chairs, a white floor lamp, a striped rug, and a gallery wall of various framed artworks above a black sofa.\" width=\"810\" height=\"951\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-12-810x951.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-12-800x939.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-12-768x902.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDespite downsizing from a larger home, the couple prioritized shared spaces over private rooms. The layout maximizes openness and flow, with communal areas taking center stage. A sheltered deck garden, perfect for summer dinners, completes the setting – a space designed for living slowly and savoring the water views.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578521\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578521\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern patio with wooden decking, potted plants, a table and chairs, and large glass doors leading to an indoor dining area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578522\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578522\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-14-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern hallway with wooden doors, a built-in bench, a wall-mounted display cabinet, a colorful rug, and a wooden staircase.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-14-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578523\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578523\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A display cabinet with shelves holding miniature models of chairs, benches, and furniture pieces in various designs and materials.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578524\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578524\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden door beside a staircase opens to reveal a wine storage room with bottles organized on shelves.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA highlight feature is the custom-designed wine cellar, lined in oak and temperature-controlled via a system that draws on the surrounding seawater. This blend of form and function exemplifies the meticulous planning behind every detail of the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578525\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578525\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden door and a built-in wooden wardrobe with simple black handles, set against white walls and a light wood floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-16m.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578526\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578526\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden staircase with white walls, wooden doors on the left, and a hallway leading to another room in a modern, minimalist interior.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eReflecting on the arrival of his floating home, Garde recalls the emotional weight of seeing it towed into place on a calm summer evening. Since then, life on the water has offered a renewed sense of serenity. The gentle motion of the home and the ever-changing light over the harbor have become part of daily life – an embodiment of Garde’s belief that thoughtful design can elevate the everyday.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578527\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578527\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bathroom with a floating wooden sink, wall-mounted faucet, framed mirror, ceramic decor, and a glass door leading to an outdoor deck.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578528\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578528\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19-810x1248.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist shower with concrete walls, brass rain showerhead, three brass controls, a handheld shower, and a built-in niche holding soap and a small item.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1248\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19-810x1248.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19-800x1233.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19-768x1183.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19-997x1536.jpg 997w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578529\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578529\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A small wooden deck with a bench and towel, a ladder leading into the water, and a concrete wall with a glass door and greenery visible outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578530\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578530\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.co