nal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-22-810x542.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bedroom with a neatly made bed, two wall-mounted reading lamps, a framed painting above the bed, and a wooden wardrobe.\" width=\"810\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-22-810x542.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-22-800x536.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-22-768x514.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578533\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578533\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bathroom with a gold sink and faucet, wall-mounted mirror with a wooden frame, and a colorful framed artwork on a white wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=578534\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-578534\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A white lifebuoy with red bands and the text \u0026#34;M/S GARDE KØBENHAVN\u0026#34; is mounted on a dark wooden wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/06/Garde-Hvalsoe-Houseboat-Copenhagen-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on Garde Hvalsøe, visit \u003ca href=\"https://gardehvalsoe.dk/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003egardehvalsoe.dk\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/birgittawolfgang/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eBirgitta Wolfgang Bjørnvad\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCa